Template: elexis/db_type
Type: select
Choices: postgresql, mysql
Default: postgresql
Description: Type of database to use. Defaults to postgresql

Template: elexis/db_server
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Name of the database server Elexis should connect to. Defaults to localhost

Template: elexis/db_names
Type: string
Default: elexis elexis_test
Description: Names of the postgresql database to create, (space separated)
 If it is empty, we will not create a PostgreSQL database.
 No support for MySQL available at this time.

Template: elexis/db_password
Type: password
Default: elexisTest
Description: Password to access the postgresql database. Defaults to elexisTest. User is elexis

